Public Repository Notice

This repository is not open source.

This repository is provided only as a public showcase and distribution space for the pre-alpha version of FrigoSmart.

FrigoSmart is a student/project app created to help users manage food in their fridge and pantry, track expiration dates, organize shopping lists, and reduce food waste.

The full source code, backend implementation, API files, database dumps, private configuration files, credentials, and development materials are not included in this repository.

Unless explicitly stated otherwise, the materials published in this repository are provided for viewing, testing, and presentation purposes only.

You may not copy, modify, redistribute, or reuse FrigoSmart project materials without explicit permission from the project authors.
